                @*<svg version="1.1" id="logo" class="navbar-brand-img brand-md" xmlns:xlink="~/Images/General_Motors_(2021).svg" xmlns="~/Images/General_Motors_(2021).svg" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 120 120" xml:space="preserve">
